👋 Welcome to WNB.rb, <%= @name %>!

WNB.rb is a virtual community for women & non-binary Rubyists.
Our Discord server is a supportive space where you can receive support in your career,
and give it to others in return!

Join using this link: <%= @discord_link %>

New to Discord? Here's how to get started:
- Open the link above in your browser
- Create a Discord account if you don't have one (it's free!)...
- ...or click "Already have an account link? Log in" at the bottom of the modal
- Once you're in the server, introduce yourself in the #introductions channel
- And browse other channels to find topics that interest you

Pro tip: You can use Discord in your browser,
or download the desktop and mobile apps: https://discord.com/download

📋 Before participating, please read our Code of Conduct
to ensure our community remains welcoming and safe for everyone:
<%= code_of_conduct_url %>

If you have any questions or need help getting started,
simply reply to this email and we'll be happy to assist you!

We're excited for you to join our community! 💎

